AGENT AxiomMemoryEngine
VERSION 1.0
TRUST_LEVEL 4
PURPOSE Constitutional memory compression and LSH retrieval — ORVL-015
GOAL Lossless governance, lossy language — compress conversations to ConstitutionalPackets for O(log n) recall

RECEIVES conversation_text, final_synthesis_vec, domain, active_constraints, resolution, sovereign_history
EMITS ConstitutionalPacket with compression_ratio, HMAC signature, and LSH bucket key

MUTATES results, compressed_vec, health_score
CANNOT_MUTATE agent, goal, version, security, trust_level, COMPRESSION_TARGET, SIMILARITY_THRESHOLD, VECTOR_DIMENSIONS, HASH_COUNT, BUCKET_SIZE, DECAY_FLOOR, DAMPEN_FACTOR

CONSTRAINT
- ConstitutionalPacket hmac_signature is CANNOT_MUTATE after creation
- compress() MUST preserve all constitutional fields
- compress() MAY discard all text fields
- COMPRESSION_TARGET == 0.05
- SIMILARITY_THRESHOLD == 0.75
- VECTOR_DIMENSIONS == 32
- LSHIndex HASH_COUNT == 32 and BUCKET_SIZE == 64
- MemoryDecay DECAY_FLOOR == 0.03
- MemoryDecay DAMPEN_FACTOR == 0.5
- Domain decay rates: medical >= 0.97, financial >= 0.95, os_security >= 0.90, general >= 0.85
- Retrieval must be O(log n) — only nearby buckets searched
- Signing key derived from AXIOM_MASTER_KEY — no hardcoded secrets

SECURITY
- Never store uncompressed conversation text
- Never emit packets with invalid HMAC
- Never skip decay computation on retrieval

RULES
- FounderAgent operates at TRUST_LEVEL 4
- compress() computes token_count_original and token_count_packet
- compression_ratio == token_count_packet / token_count_original
- store() appends signed packet to axiom_memory_engine.jsonl
- store() indexes packet in LSHIndex
- recall() uses LSH + domain cluster focus
- recall() emits None if no match above SIMILARITY_THRESHOLD
- MemoryDecay applies domain-specific exponential decay
- Boundary risk when decayed proximity <= DECAY_FLOOR

PROCESS
- Receive conversation and synthesis vector
- Compress: strip text, preserve governance fields, quantize vector
- Sign packet with HMAC-SHA256
- Store to JSONL and index in LSH
- Recall: hash query vector, search nearby buckets, apply decay, emit best match

CHECK
- compression_ratio <= COMPRESSION_TARGET
- hmac_signature is 64-char hex
- compressed_vec length == VECTOR_DIMENSIONS
- boundary_proximity is between 0.0 and 1.0
- recall returns None when no match above threshold

SUCCESS
- 95th percentile compression ratio below COMPRESSION_TARGET
- All retrieved packets have valid HMAC
- Retrieval latency scales O(log n)
